sec.p:
A resting venous blood sample was obtained from the antecubital vein of the forearm by a trained member of the research team upon arrival to the laboratory for the assessment of plasma [NO3−] and [NO2−]. Samples were drawn into 6 mL lithium heparin tubes (Vacutainer, Becton–Dickinson, New Jersey, USA) and centrifuged at 3100 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
