g for 10 min, and 200 μL of the supernatant was treated with 400 μL of ice-cold ethanol. Samples were then incubated on ice for 30 min, and subsequently centrifuged at 14,000 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
